message.body: Hi! Who goes up next at Last Drop? Did I misunderstand and did Annie want me to stay up There for two months? She said to stay up at Crane two months originally
(I will call her too, but just wanted to check in w you first.)
My understanding was Annie had the next show.
Yep and so I think she wanted more time
I'll check in w her but I think I stay up two months?
I'm at work right now, so I prolly can't take that call, but lemme know.

Also, I'm meeting w/ some folks soon for later shows (Adam C, Katie and maybe Jen), but we really gotta finalize w/ Thom and Matt. Need to know when Annie wants to go up so we can schedule spring/finalize winter.
Oh, and also Kenny too. So I've got four potential artists to meet up with.
